comments: Definitely miss having her at FPU...

Science has never been a strength of mine & I was not looking forward to this class/lab, but I learned a great deal, & many of the assigments to my surprise, were interesting. The lectures were on a rotating basis, & hers were by far the best. Outside of class, she was extremely compassionate & helped w/ adjusting to college life. Highly recommend!

Some people dont like her but I had no problem with her. She was always nice, and easy going. The lab reports she gives are time consuming but not difficult. Overall, she is a good prof. to have for lab.
She\'s a great sci prof. Best one to have required science with. very down to earth and makes concepts easier to understand. great for lab and lecture.
